cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.CV, cs.PL 

This paper deals with artificial intelligence, machine learning, and game theory, which are all covered by the cs.AI and cs.LG categories. The use of probability distributions over random seeds and the application to Phantom Go involve computer vision techniques, which are covered by the cs.CV category. Finally, the learning of an opening book involves planning and decision-making, which are covered by the cs.PL category.
